: : Darkangel : :

Darkangel: Oh, hello there. Yeah, I've been out for awhile. Where is the commander?


airly2000 <airly2002@...> wrote:
Vamprah:

"Hi fellows, long time without see ya"said a femenine voice 


> : : DeathStar : :
>  
> Within his quarters at the Tripred base, DeathStar awakes from a 
long sleep. He opens a commlink to Darkangel.
>  
> DeathStar(via comm): Darkangel, you read?
>  
> The comm message awakes Darkangel who had fallen asleep at his 
station on the Tripred bridge. He opens a return channel.
>  
> Darkangel(via comm): Yeah, I read you. I guess I had fellen asleep.
>  
> DeathStar: Odd, so did I. Any idea whats going on?
>  
> Darkangel: Let me find out.
>  
> Darkangel closes the channel and turns to a bridge officer.
>  
> Darkangel: Where is the commander?
>
